name: Roasted Millet Curls

name: Multimillet Cookies
description: Munch Fit Healthy, Tasty & Crunchy Multimillet Cookies | Jowar, Ragi & Bajra Cookies | 100% Natural & Healthy Cookies | Gluten Free | No Maida, No Added Sugar | Made with Desi Khaand. HEALTHY & CRUNCHY MULTIMILLET COOKIES: These healthy cookies are made up of Jowar, Ragi, Bajra, Almonds & Desi Khaand, hence relish these delightful Multimillet Cookies - a delectable blend of flavors and crunchy goodness.
